  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK647">
<l>colalvallaṉ cōrvila ṉañcā ṉavaṉai </l>
<l> yikalvellal yārkku maritu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is impossible for any one to conquer him by intrique who possesses power of speech, and is neither faulty nor timid.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
